casebody.data:
Thursday, December 9, 1999

DISCIPLINARY DOCKET

99-1557. Columbus Bar Assn. v. Saker.

Upon consideration of respondent’s motion for leave to file a post-hearing brief and relator’s motion to strike respondent’s motion for leave to file a post-hearing brief,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion for leave to file a post-hearing brief be, and hereby is, denied.
